# Bug Investigation & Root Cause Tracing

## Overview

Bugs manifest deep in call stacks. Your instinct: fix where the error appears. That treats symptoms.

**Goal:** Trace backward through the call chain until you find the original trigger. Fix at source.

**NOT for:**

- New feature delivery → use [build.md](build.md)
- Unknown problems or uncertainty → use [investigate.md](investigate.md)
- Delivered features needing tweaks → use [refine.md](refine.md)
- Code quality concerns → use [refactor.md](refactor.md)

**Outputs:**

- Failing test reproducing the bug
- Fix applied at root cause
- Defence-in-depth validation (for complex bugs)
- Updated documentation (if design/plan affected)

