## The Process

### Non-Negotiable Rules

<CRITICAL_REQUIREMENT type="MANDATORY">

- You MUST write a failing test reproducing the bug before fixing
- You MUST READ `/midtempo-framework/rules/testing.md` before writing any test
- You MUST verify all compliance gates ({{ testing_cg_range() }}) from `/midtempo-framework/rules/testing.md` on the reproducing test
- You MUST READ `/midtempo-framework/instructions/error-handling.md` if the bug involves error handling, API failures, or error UI states
- You MUST trace to root cause before fixing — never fix at the symptom point
- You MUST evaluate complexity to determine if defence-in-depth is required
