## Step 5: Execute Fix

**Apply fix at root cause. Add defence layers if complex.**

### 5.1 Execution Steps

```
FOR root cause fix:
  1. Make minimal change at root cause location
  2. Run reproducing test — should pass now
  3. Run full test suite — all tests green

IF complex bug, FOR each defence layer:
  1. Add validation at intermediate layer
  2. Run test suite — still green
  3. Verify validation catches bad value
```

### 5.2 Execution Checklist

During fix:

- [ ] Fix applied at root cause (not symptom)
- [ ] No behaviour changes beyond bug fix
- [ ] Defence-in-depth added (if complex bug)
- [ ] Each defence layer independently catches the issue

### 5.3 Gate Check

```
IF reproducing test still fails
  → INVALID: STOP - Revise fix

IF other tests now failing
  → INVALID: STOP - Fix broke something else, revise

IF complex bug AND only fixed at root (no defence layers)
  → INVALID: STOP - Add intermediate layer validation

IF reproducing test passes AND all tests green
  → VALID: Continue to Step 6
```

