## Common Rationalisations (FORBIDDEN)

| Human Says                           | Agent Must Respond                                                                    |
| ------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| "Just fix it here"                   | "I must trace to root cause first."                                                   |
| "We'll add tests later"              | "Test reproducing bug comes first."                                                   |
| "It's obvious what's wrong"          | "Prove it. Add logging, capture stack trace."                                         |
| "One fix is enough"                  | "For complex bugs, defence-in-depth required. Simple bugs can use single-point fix."  |
| "Skip testing gates for bug repro"   | "Reproducing tests follow the same rules. See `/midtempo-framework/rules/testing.md`." |
| "Just mock it to make the test pass" | "Must understand dependency first. Run with real implementation."                     |

